<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649660>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 6. Fimbriosthenelais zetlandica (McIntosh, 1876). TUM 39480 (A–B, D–E) and SMF 12682 (C, F–H). A. Anterior end, palps not figured, bent downwards. B. Right elytron of segment 5. C. Detail of posterior elytral margin. D. Left parapodium of segment 13, anterior view. E. Same, posterior view. F–H. Neurochaetae of segment 11, all distal part. F. Upper compound falciger. G. Middle compound falciger. H. Lower compound falciger. Scale bars: A, D–E =500 µm; B =1 mm; C, F–H=100 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4649660/files/figure.png" .

